name: Samuel Alebachew
tagline: My personal website for blogs, projects, and other information that obviously care about.
body:
### Welcome
My name is Samuel Alebachew, a computer engineer with interests spanning over distant subjects from beer, outdoor activities, people/relationships, all STEM fields and especially (obviously) computer science. This page is where I get to show people what I don't know, what I think I know, and what I have done with what I think I know. Surprisingly, you can do a lot with just that much. This page is very new and I will be making several changes quite often. Thanks for stopping by! 

### Support or Contact
Want to say hi? Feel free to email me at samuel (dot) alebachew (at) gmail. :)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
